<div align="center">
<h1>BALLView 1.3 Documentation</h1>
<p align="justify">BALLView is a free molecular modeling and
molecular graphics tool. It provides fast OpenGL-based
visualization of molecular structures, molecular mechanics methods
(minimization, MD simulation using the AMBER, CHARMM, and MMFF94
force fields), molecular editing, as well as calculation and
visualization of electrostatic properties (FDPB).</p>
</div>
